    drexelVS1¶

    Participants | Proceedings | Input | Appendix

    • Run ID: drexelVS1
    • Participant: dragon
    • Track: Federated Web Search
    • Year: 2014
    • Submission: 8/19/2014
    • Task: vertical

    FW14Docs100¶

    • Year: 2014
